{"tid":37074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要下屬改電腦隱瞞遲返工 前警長判罰服務令","createTime":"2016-12-13T06:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T03:28:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"914b5012e5e658a537f6b77902c946b3e4087f02","tid":37074,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:18:26.000Z","msg":"曾任警署警長的港鐵特檢隊男主管屢因遲起床或要吃早餐而遲上班，但卻152次要求下屬在公司系統代為輸入虛假的上班時間，「遲到大王」早前承認6項不誠實地意圖欺騙而取用電腦罪，今在裁判法院被判160小時社會服務令。 <br />\n<br />\n辯方大律師貝敦指，男被告黃成根（63歲）已找到新工作。早前求情指他任職保安員。被告案發時是港鐵「附例特檢隊」主管，入職港鐵前曾任警署警長。據案情透露，他曾要下屬代他輸入虛假上時，訛稱9時許抵達上水站開工，但實情下午1時才在美孚站啟程上班。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161213/56041449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161213%2F56041449&d=MZbb6wOW8NUOP6KiUv6%2B8AT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f1800516\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161213%2F56041449&h=1aa0a341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161213/56041449</a>"},{"pid":"44074c9d04b41cf3a9807424b9d24deaa0c17fd9","tid":37074,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:19:42.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"a03f3a49a2d838c4701a963eedffa7206c6d1d8b","tid":37074,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:20:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ceb6d3673ca0a43c6a61ca7f5c607f2e5c756369","tid":37074,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:22:13.000Z","msg":"唔止㗎喎<br />\n改嗰條友都要拉啦"},{"pid":"c034ab0744e4fecba6a622f0dd0098dc1eb70ee2","tid":37074,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:32:08.000Z","msg":"退休警無得撈，好大機會為非作歹"},{"pid":"cbd719187017121cbd9b023e224180ab1b064583","tid":37074,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:40:29.000Z","msg":"聽聞港鐵會check員工八達通使用時間<br />\